{"tid":2443404,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲研究指偏見與智力有關  智商越低越大機會歧視同性戀","createTime":"2021-03-12T04:56:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T05:04:16.000Z","uid":125489,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3e0956bda94d90c132018fa389f1099d0660037b","tid":2443404,"uid":125489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T04:56:51.000Z","msg":"現代社會發展快速，不少往時的封閉觀念一一被打破，反對種族﹑性別﹑性取向歧視的聲音愈見主流，聯合國教育﹑科學與文化組織亦主張「不分種族﹑性別﹑語言或宗教的人均享有人權和自由」。以同性戀為例，雖然早於20世紀世界各國已將同性戀除罪化，近在台灣亦於2019年將同性婚姻合法化，但世上仍然有不少民眾無法接受同性傾向的群眾。澳洲的昆士蘭大學日前發表有關偏見﹑歧視的研究報告，結果顯示對同性戀的偏見和智商或有相關性，IQ愈低的人，愈大機會持有偏見。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲昆士蘭大學日前公開一份研究報告，以11,564個澳洲人為研究對象，分別以受訪者的家庭收入﹑勞動力以及問卷答案作分析，問卷內容包括對受訪者認知能力評估以及其對平等權利的看法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://travel.ulifestyle.com.hk/news/detail/34939/%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%8C%87%E5%81%8F%E8%A6%8B%E8%88%87%E6%99%BA%E5%8A%9B%E6%9C%89%E9%97%9C-%E6%99%BA%E5%95%86%E8%B6%8A%E4%BD%8E%E8%B6%8A%E5%A4%A7%E6%A9%9F%E6%9C%83%E6%AD%A7%E8%A6%96%E5%90%8C%E6%80%A7%E6%88%80/1?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_content=link&amp;fbclid=IwAR30VMEyPsatmuxXNUaO2AZoh4_0pkSBCiS8XGkW7uUCIVYjGwhWDmrW_zE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftravel.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F34939%2F%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%2581%258F%25E8%25A6%258B%25E8%2588%2587%25E6%2599%25BA%25E5%258A%259B%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%2597%259C-%25E6%2599%25BA%25E5%2595%2586%25E8%25B6%258A%25E4%25BD%258E%25E8%25B6%258A%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%25AD%25A7%25E8%25A6%2596%25E5%2590%258C%25E6%2580%25A7%25E6%2588%2580%2F1%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_content%3Dlink%26fbclid%3DIwAR30VMEyPsatmuxXNUaO2AZoh4_0pkSBCiS8XGkW7uUCIVYjGwhWDmrW_zE&d=RGPktlJYpqjIeXpZRAkgwwwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=05b6a51d\" target=\"_blank\">https://travel.ulifestyle.com.hk/news/detail/34939/%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%8C%87%E5%81%8F%E8%A6%8B%E8%88%87%E6%99%BA%E5%8A%9B%E6%9C